00:07:51.540 --> 00:07:54.580
is one of the most
predictive markers of aging

00:07:54.580 --> 00:07:57.830
and biological aging and no
surprise that is governed

00:07:57.830 --> 00:08:00.760
by the brain to muscle connection.

00:08:00.760 --> 00:08:05.320
